title: Unmei no Kiss wa Oazuke
original_name: 運命のキスはおあずけ
sinopse:
Nanao, an omega, is working in the nightlife business, but he hates the arrogant Alphas. Arisaka is a serious Alpha that was brought by his co-worker into Nanao's workplace. The two have an argument but as soon as Nanao touches him, his heat suddenly came up.

(Source: MU)

Included one-shot: As you like, Master
